<div id="banner">
	<h1>How iTMS Works</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>I just finished writing <a href="../2002/itms/index.html">Behind the iTunes Music Store: A Technical Description of iTMS and FairPlay</a>. As you might guess, it explains how the iTunes Music Store works, including the only human-readable description of how FairPlay, Apple&#8217;s DRM system, works. Get it before the government does!</p>

<p>Comments, corrections, and additions are appreciated. Also, I&#8217;m looking for a way to intercept and decrypt SSL traffic.</p>

<p class="posted">posted March 29, 2004 04:20 PM (<a class="category" href="http://www.aaronsw.com/weblog/cat_technology">Technology</a>) (<a href="001193#comments">2 comments</a>) <a href="001193" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
</div>

